text.tspan: MoveTo: M x y | m dx dy
LineTo: L x y | l dx dy
Horizontal line: H x | h dx
Vertical Line: V y | v dy
Bezier: C x1 y1, x2 y2, x y // Cubic; x,y - line end; x1,y1,x2,y2 - control points
Bezier: S x2 y2, x y // shortcut for C: if S follows C or S, => x1,y1 reflect the previous x2,y2; otherwise x1=x2,y1=y2 (same control points)
Bezier: Q x1 y1, x y // Quadratic; x1,y1 - control point; x,y - line end
Bezier: T x y // shortcut for Q; control point inferred from the previous one; if not after Q or T, control point = previous point (draws a line)
Arc: A rx ry kierunek-osi-x 0-łuk-<-180-stopni-1-otherwise large-arc-flag 0-łuk-w-lewo-1-łuk-w-prawo x y rx,ry elliptical radius
